<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@4.0.1/dist/flowbite.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body class="bg-[#1c2541] text-[#FBFFFF] font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif overflow-visible">
   <nav>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between mx-auto p-4">
    <a href="#" class="flex items-center space-x-2">
      <img src="/assets/Logo.png" class="flex-auto ml-9 w-16 h-18" alt="TenantFlow Logo" />
      <span class="text-xl font-semibold">TenantFlow</span>
    </a>
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-20 text-[#adb5bd]">
      <a href="#accordion-open" class="hover:text-blue-600 text-xl">How it works</a>
      <a href="/login.html" class="hover:text-blue-600 text-xl">Login</a>
      <a href="/register.html" class="px-3 py-2 text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg">
        Get Started
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">
      Manage your team in one secure workspace
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
      A multi-tenant SaaS platform for teams to collaborate, manage tasks, and scale securely.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
      <a href="/register.html" class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">
        Create Workspace
      </a>
      <a href="/login.html" class="px-6 py-3 border border-blue-600 text-blue-600 rounded-lg">
        Login
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="features" class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10">Core features</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg">
        🔐 Secure authentication & roles
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg">
        🏢 Organization-based workspaces
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg">
        📁 Project & task management
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg">
        🛡️ Tenant-isolated data
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<div id="accordion-open" data-accordion="open" class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto border border-default overflow-hidden shadow-xs px-20 text-grey-4 align-center">
  <h2 id="accordion-open-heading-1">
    <button type="button" class="flex items-center w-full justify-between p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-body rounded-t-base border border-t-0 border-x-0 border-b-default hover:text-heading hover:bg-neutral-secondary-medium gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-open-body-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-open-body-1">
      <span class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.529 9.988a2.502 2.502 0 1 1 5 .191A2.441 2.441 0 0 1 12 12.582V14m-.01 3.008H12M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>What is a workspace?</span>
      <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-5 h-5 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m5 15 7-7 7 7"/></svg>
    </button>
  </h2>
  <div id="accordion-open-body-1" class="hidden border border-s-0 border-e-0 border-t-0 border-b-default text-[#ADB2BA]" aria-labelledby="accordion-open-heading-1">
    <div class="p-4 md:p-5">
      <p class="mb-2 text-body">A workspace represents your organization on the platform.
It acts as a secure environment where your team, projects, and data are managed together under one owner</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h2 id="accordion-open-heading-2">
    <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-body border border-x-0 border-b-default border-t-0 hover:text-heading hover:bg-neutral-secondary-medium gap-3 " data-accordion-target="#accordion-open-body-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-open-body-2">
      <span class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.529 9.988a2.502 2.502 0 1 1 5 .191A2.441 2.441 0 0 1 12 12.582V14m-.01 3.008H12M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>How do teams and roles work?</span>
      <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-5 h-5 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m5 15 7-7 7 7"/></svg>
    </button>
  </h2>
  <div id="accordion-open-body-2" class="hidden border border-s-0 border-e-0 border-t-0 border-b-default text-[#ADB2BA]" aria-labelledby="accordion-open-heading-2">
    <div class="p-4 md:p-5">
      <p class="mb-2 text-body">Team members are invited into a workspace and assigned roles such as owner, admin, or member.
These roles control what actions users can perform, ensuring secure and organized collaboration.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="accordion-open-heading-3">
    <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-body border border-x-0 border-b-default border-t-0 hover:text-heading hover:bg-neutral-secondary-medium gap-3 " data-accordion-target="#accordion-open-body-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-open-body-3">
      <span class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.529 9.988a2.502 2.502 0 1 1 5 .191A2.441 2.441 0 0 1 12 12.582V14m-.01 3.008H12M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>How is data kept secure between organizations?</span>
      <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-5 h-5 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m5 15 7-7 7 7"/></svg>
    </button>
  </h2>
  <div id="accordion-open-body-3" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-open-heading-3">
    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 border border-t-default border-b-0 border-x-0 ">
      <p class="mb-2 text-body">Each workspace has its own isolated data scope.
Projects and tasks created in one workspace are completely separated from other organizations on the platform.</p>
      <ul class="ps-5 text-body list-disc">
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="accordion-open-heading-4">
    <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-body  hover:text-heading hover:bg-neutral-secondary-medium gap-3 " data-accordion-target="#accordion-open-body-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-open-body-4">
      <span class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.529 9.988a2.502 2.502 0 1 1 5 .191A2.441 2.441 0 0 1 12 12.582V14m-.01 3.008H12M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>Can I manage multiple organizations or workspaces?</span>
      <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-5 h-5 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m5 15 7-7 7 7"/></svg>
    </button>
  </h2>
  <div id="accordion-open-body-4" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-open-heading-4">
    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 border border-t-default border-b-0 border-x-0 ">
      <p class="mb-2 text-body">Yes. You can create and manage multiple workspaces, each with its own team, projects, and data.
This makes it easy to separate work across different organizations or clients while using the same platform.</p>
      <ul class="ps-5 text-body list-disc">
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<section class="py-16 ">
  <div class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Common use cases</h2>
    <ul class="divide-y divide-gray-200 border rounded-lg text-[#FBFFFF]">
      <li class="p-4">Teams managing internal projects</li>
      <li class="p-4">Organizations with role-based access needs</li>
      <li class="p-4">Agencies managing multiple client workspaces</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 ">
  <div class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="p-4 text-sm text-blue-800 border border-blue-300 rounded-lg bg-blue-50">
      Built with a secure, scalable, multi-tenant backend architecture designed for real-world SaaS platforms.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



